dc_description_s: This point shapefile represents populated places within the United States that include both census designated places and incorporated places identified by the U.S. Census. Data are represented at a 1:250,000 scale. This layer is part of the 2014 ESRI Data and Maps collection for ArcGIS 10.2.U.S. Populated Place Points provides locations for populated places including fieldsâ€”name, FIPS code, Census class, population, and selected demographic data from the U.S. Census.
